{"tid":552211,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"圍爐","createTime":"2018-02-06T10:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T14:30:06.000Z","uid":45206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7b670947b0800dfa0a2d5fdea3f857a38f28fcbf","tid":552211,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T10:05:46.000Z","msg":"輸好多錢 收工行下行下忍唔住係條街喊咗<br />\n<br />\n我垃圾 我無用 我廢<br />\n<br />\n收市之後已經無覆過任何人message, pop up message 見到朋友討論點媾仔 去邊食好西 新年去邊道旅行 無任何意慾參與討論 <br />\n<br />\n為咗錢去市場搏大细 人又蠢 未能洞悉前機 輸身家 自作自受 正仆街"},{"pid":"484c08b9f0f991bb9664d650caebb957331a9433","tid":552211,"uid":94551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"買咩？"},{"pid":"358eef160e1d763d6bb0ff163e8ae4a00af08efc","tid":552211,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T10:07:24.000Z","msg":"輸幾多呀 輸左咪贏返返黎<br />\n唔洗咁灰嘅"},{"pid":"4b619434cc453b1c43d04ead12eddbb73a824b27","tid":552211,"uid":37130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會忘記昨日.. <br />\n<br />\n已經四日沒有股票升，昨晚終於忍不住，真的很肚餓，餓到連尊嚴也不顧... <br />\n沒有辦法，身上已無分文，屋企人又唔理，又找不到工作，連八達通的五十蚊按金也拿走了.. <br />\n<br />\n吃二手飯的感覺真的很難堪，昨晚在某屋村的大家樂，吃了別人剩下的飯餸，理不了別人的目光，一邊食眼淚俏俏的在眼角滴下......我是一個窮撚"},{"pid":"804a6441f0d4099c966e09f91b4a72ef0c29c16b","tid":552211,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484c08b9f0f991bb9664d650caebb957331a9433","tid":552211,"uid":94551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"買咩？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"騰訊近價short put"},{"pid":"6185f198ad8066dc5dc8955eb474121a0085a0fc","tid":552211,"uid":43650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T10:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/180954_cb3eba4b643ce670ed63e574a6b7a7ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F